Altice USA



	Altice USA is one of the largest broadband communications and video services providers in the United States. The company delivers broadband, pay television, telephony services, Wi-Fi hotspot access, proprietary content and advertising services to approximately 4.9 million residential and business customers. Our employees have an unwavering commitment to customers and to providing quality products and outstanding services.
 



    We make
    our dreams reality.




